{"tid":284452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬頭角道旅巴撞兩男女 捲入車底1死1傷","createTime":"2017-06-15T02:38:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-15T03:13:20.000Z","uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"56cfa3ccedce591e34643f5a822dd97f5b9cd796","tid":284452,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T02:38:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170615/56830397\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170615%2F56830397&d=z9kzH8MKTQWsgj0QUwzsjDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=7a26432b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170615%2F56830397&h=bdb04cb9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170615/56830397</a><br />\n<br />\n【10:26更新】兩名傷者中，一人傷重不治，另一人送廣華醫院搶救。<br />\n<br />\n早上10時許，土瓜灣馬頭角道欣榮花園對開發生交通意外。現場消息稱，一輛載客旅遊巴，沿馬頭角道行駛，駛過北帝街街口時撞倒一男一女，並將他們捲入車底。大批消防員在場拯救，10多分鐘後先後將兩名傷者救出，惟其中一人當場不治，另一人滿面鮮血送廣華醫院搶救。<br />\n現場有小巴司機指出，涉事旅遊巴衝燈，警方正在場展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170615/large/1497492727_4357.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170615%2Flarge%2F1497492727_4357.jpg&h=02a090fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2469b1d277bcea6d9467f5e2974a9d7095f626c3","tid":284452,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T02:40:15.000Z","msg":"係咪載強國旅行團果d大巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14df3171ae98e86e370a4255900a9eb11b948cb0","tid":284452,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T02:42:59.000Z","msg":"呢個位衝燈同碌拎全中一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35c5c67de0354320a390cc0bdc2c9818a098b2e5","tid":284452,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T02: